《[[美国骗局|美国骗局]]》是一部[[2013年电影|2013年]]的[[美国电影|美国]][[喜剧片|喜剧]][[犯罪片|犯罪]][[剧情片|剧情片]]，由[[大卫·欧·拉塞尔|大卫·欧·拉塞尔]]执导并和埃里克·沃伦·辛格（{{lang|en|Eric Warren Singer}}）共同[[编剧|编剧]]，根据20世纪70年代末到80年代初[[美国联邦调查局|美国联邦调查局]]的[[阿布斯坎|阿布斯坎]]（{{lang|en|ABSCAM}}）行动改编。电影在[[波士顿|波士顿]]、[[伍斯特_(马萨诸塞州)|伍斯特]]和[[纽约|纽约]]取景，主要演员包括[[克里斯蒂安·贝尔|克里斯蒂安·贝尔]]、[[艾美·亚当斯|艾美·亚当斯]]、[[布莱德利·库珀|布莱德利·库珀]]、[[杰瑞米·雷纳|杰瑞米·雷纳]]和[[詹妮弗·劳伦斯|詹妮弗·劳伦斯]]。

[[哥伦比亚电影公司|哥伦比亚电影公司]]从2013年12月13日开始在6家电影院限量放映《美国骗局》，12月20日再开始在美国和加拿大的超过2500家电影院全面上映<ref name="BOM" />。影片以4000万[[美元|美元]]的拍摄预算获得了超过2.51亿美元的全球[[票房|票房]]<ref name="BOM">{{cite web | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=davido2013.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140614044219/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=davido2013.htm | title = American Hustle (2013) | publisher = IMDB.com | work = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | accessdate = 2014-06-19 | archivedate = 2014-06-14 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，创下了拉塞尔作品商业收益的新纪录<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?view=Director&id=davidorussell.htm | title = David O. Russell Movie Box Office Results | publisher = IMDB.com | work = Box Office Mojo | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325144215/http://boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?view=Director&id=davidorussell.htm | accessdate = 2014-06-19 | archivedate = 2014-03-25}}</ref>。根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上收集的245篇评论文章，其中有228篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，新鲜度达93%，平均评分8.2（最高10分）<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-06-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140605104205/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/american_hustle/ | deadurl = no | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/american_hustle/ | title = American Hustle | publisher = Flixster | work = Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate = 2014-06-19}}</ref>；而在{{lang|en|[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}上收集的47篇评论中则有46篇给出好评，1篇褒贬不一，综合评分90（最高100）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.metacritic.com/movie/american-hustle | title = American Hustle | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140617094652/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/american-hustle | publisher = CBS | work = Metacritic | accessdate = 2014-06-19 | archivedate = 2014-06-17 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

在[[第86届奥斯卡金像奖|第86届奥斯卡金像奖]]角逐中，《美国骗局》和《[[地心引力_(电影)|地心引力]]》均以10项提名领跑<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-american-hustle-gravity-score-671461 | title = Oscars: 'American Hustle,' 'Gravity' Score 10 Nominations Each | work = The Hollywood Reporter | publisher = Prometheus Global Media | date = 2014-01-16 | accessdate = 2014-06-19 | archivedate = 2014-05-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140517235844/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-american-hustle-gravity-score-671461}}</ref>，并且成为[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]历史上第15部获得全部4项演员类奖项提名的电影<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140311053846/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-25711514 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-25711514 | title = American Hustle and Gravity vie for Oscars | publisher = BBC News | date = 2014-01-16 | accessdate = 2014-06-19 | archivedate = 2014-03-11}}</ref>，但最终这10项提名均未能获奖<ref>{{cite news | url = http://variety.com/2014/film/news/oscars-the-biggest-snubs-and-surprises-of-the-night-1201124074/ | title = Oscars: The Biggest Snubs of the Night | work = [[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]] | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | date = 2014-03-02 | accessdate = 2014-06-19 | archivedate = 2014-03-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140308205929/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/oscars-the-biggest-snubs-and-surprises-of-the-night-1201124074/}}</ref>。在[[第71届金球奖|第71届金球奖]]角逐中，影片获得了7项提名，最终有[[金球奖最佳音乐及喜剧电影|最佳影片（音乐剧/喜剧类）]]（艾米·亚当斯）、[[金球奖最佳音乐及喜剧类电影女主角|最佳电影女主角（音乐剧/喜剧类）]]和[[金球奖最佳电影女配角|最佳女配角奖]]（詹妮弗·劳伦斯）三项胜出<ref name="GGnom">{{cite news | url = http://variety.com/2014/film/awards/2014-golden-globes-nominee-list-1200948220/ | title = Golden Globes Nominations: The Full List | work = Variety | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | date = 2014-01-11 | accessdate = 2014-06-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140329144547/http://variety.com/2014/film/awards/2014-golden-globes-nominee-list-1200948220/ | archivedate = 2014-03-29 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="GGwin">{{cite news | archivedate = 2014-05-21 | deadurl = no | url = http://variety.com/2014/film/news/golden-globe-awards-winners-2014-list-golden-globes-1201050486/ | title = Golden Globe Awards Winners | work = Variety | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | date = 2014-01-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140521123452/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/golden-globe-awards-winners-2014-list-golden-globes-1201050486/ | accessdate = 2014-06-19}}</ref>。《美国骗局》获得了10项[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]提名，最终赢得了原著剧本奖和化妆与发型奖的同时，还为劳伦斯赢得了[[英国电影学院奖最佳女配角|最佳女配角奖]]<ref name="BAFTAnom">{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140619091952/http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/afi-awards-2013-film-winners-full-list/ | url = http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a541988/bafta-film-awards-2014-nominations-in-full.html | title = BAFTA Film Awards 2014 – nominations in full|publisher= Digital Spy | date = 2014-01-08 | accessdate = 2014-06-19 | archivedate = 2014-06-19}}</ref><ref name="BAFTAwin">{{cite web | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-26218678 | title = Bafta Film Awards 2014: Full list of winners | publisher = BBC News | date = 2014-02-16 | accessdate = 2014-06-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140220052409/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-26218678 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-02-20}}</ref>。影片还在[[第20届美国演员工会奖|第20届]][[美国演员工会奖|美国演员工会奖]]角逐中获得了群体演出奖<ref name="SAGwin">{{cite web | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-25800667 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140207183448/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-25800667 | title = SAG Awards 2014: Winners in Full | publisher = BBC News | date = 2014-01-19 | accessdate = 2014-06-19 | archivedate = 2014-02-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，并获[[美国导演工会奖|美国导演工会奖]]<ref name="DGnom">{{cite news | archivedate = 2014-01-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140107221700/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/01/07/directors-guild-awards-nominations_n_4556149.html | url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/01/07/directors-guild-awards-nominations_n_4556149.html | title = Directors Guild Awards Nominate Steve McQueen, Alfonso Cuaron, Martin Scorsese | work = The Huffington Post | publisher = AOL | date = 2014-01-07 | accessdate = 2014-06-19 | deadurl = no}}</ref>、制片人工会奖<ref name="PGnom">{{cite web | publisher = Rotten Tomatoes | date = 2014-01-02 | accessdate = 2014-06-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140201103437/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1929314/news/1929314/2014-producers-guild-awards-nominations/ | title = 2014 Producers Guild Awards Nominations | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-02-01 | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1929314/news/1929314/2014-producers-guild-awards-nominations/}}</ref>和[[美国编剧工会奖|编剧工会奖]]提名<ref name="WGnom">{{cite news | archivedate = 2014-06-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140619093517/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/moviesnow/la-et-mn-wga-awards-2014-complete-list-nominees-story.html | title = WGA Awards 2014: Complete list of winners and nominees | url = http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/moviesnow/la-et-mn-wga-awards-2014-complete-list-nominees-story.html#axzz2sHfoUX00&page=1 | work = Los Angeles Times | date = 2014-01-30 | accessdate = 2014-06-19}}</ref>。[[美国电影学会|美国电影学会]]将本片列入2013年十大佳片榜单<ref name="AFI">{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-06-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140619091952/http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/afi-awards-2013-film-winners-full-list/ | url = http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/afi-awards-2013-film-winners-full-list/ | title = AFI Awards 2013: Top 10 Films List Is Good News For Major Studios | publisher = Deadline.com | date = 2014-12-09 | accessdate = 2014-06-19}}</ref>。

